	| See the Pen <a href='http://codepen.io/jameskolce/pen/aOgZgE/'>Grid rows - Concise Framework</a> on <a href='http://codepen.io'>CodePen</a>.


h2 Columns

p
	| Columns are nested inside of rows, and can be created either by using
	| the <code>column</code> attribute or by using the <code>column()</code> mixin.

p
	| When using the <code>column()</code> mixin, you must supply an argument for
	| the size of the column, this being a fraction of a number from 0 to 1
	| <small>(<b>e.g.</b> 1/6)</small>.


p.note
	| By default, all columns collapse into 100% width at <b>48em</b>.

